{"data":{"markdownRemark":null,"npmPackage":{"name":"gatsby-remark-codemirror","description":"CodeMirror syntax highlighting plugin for Remark and Gatsby","keywords":["gatsby","gatsby-plugin","codemirror","remark"],"lastPublisher":{"name":"maxd","avatar":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/42bcec88b9653a5c34e35a2be102e115"},"repository":{"url":"https://github.com/maxdesiatov/gatsby-remark-codemirror"},"readme":{"childMarkdownRemark":{"html":"<h1 id=\"gatsby-remark-codemirror\"><a href=\"#gatsby-remark-codemirror\" aria-label=\"gatsby remark codemirror permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>gatsby-remark-codemirror</h1>\n<p>Adds syntax highlighting to code blocks in your Gatsby Markdown files using\n<a href=\"https://codemirror.net\">CodeMirror</a> <a href=\"https://codemirror.net/demo/runmode.html\">Mode\nRunner</a>. Note that this\n<a href=\"https://github.com/remarkjs/remark/blob/master/doc/plugins.md\">Remark plugin</a>\ndoes not convert your code blocks to code editor instances, only uses\nCodeMirrorâ€™s syntax highlighting engine to render static\n<code class=\"language-text\">&lt;code&gt;&lt;pre&gt;...&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;</code> blocks with appropriate CSS classes for <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;span/&gt;</code>\ntags contained within.</p>\n<h2 id=\"install\"><a href=\"#install\" aria-label=\"install permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Install</h2>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">npm install --save gatsby-transformer-remark gatsby-remark-codemirror</code></p>\n<h2 id=\"how-to-use\"><a href=\"#how-to-use\" aria-label=\"how to use permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>How to use</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// In your gatsby-config.js</span>\nplugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-transformer-remark`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n          resolve<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token template-string\"><span class=\"token string\">`gatsby-remark-codemirror`</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n          options<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">// CSS class suffix to be used for produced `&lt;pre/>` blocks.</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">// Default value is \"default\", which adds \"cm-s-default\" class.</span>\n            <span class=\"token comment\">// This class name matches</span>\n            theme<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"default\"</span>\n          <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"include-css\"><a href=\"#include-css\" aria-label=\"include css permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Include CSS</h3>\n<h4 id=\"required-pick-a-codemirror-theme-or-create-your-own\"><a href=\"#required-pick-a-codemirror-theme-or-create-your-own\" aria-label=\"required pick a codemirror theme or create your own permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Required: Pick a CodeMirror theme or create your own</h4>\n<p>CodeMirror ships with a number of <a href=\"https://github.com/codemirror/CodeMirror/tree/master/theme\">themes</a> (previewable on the <a href=\"https://codemirror.net/index.html\">CodeMirror\nwebsite</a>) that you can easily include in your Gatsby site, or you can build\nyour own by copying and modifying an example.</p>\n<p>To load a theme, just require its CSS file in your <code class=\"language-text\">gatsby-browser.js</code> file, e.g.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-browser.js</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"codemirror/lib/codemirror.css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<p>or for a non-default theme:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"javascript\"><pre class=\"language-javascript\"><code class=\"language-javascript\"><span class=\"token comment\">// gatsby-browser.js</span>\n<span class=\"token function\">require</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"codemirror/theme/ambiance.css\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">// don't forget to set `theme: \"ambiance\"` in gatsby-config.js</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3 id=\"usage-in-markdown\"><a href=\"#usage-in-markdown\" aria-label=\"usage in markdown permalink\" class=\"anchor\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Usage in Markdown</h3>\n<p>This is some beautiful code:</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">```swift\nextension Never: Equatable {\n  public static func == (lhs: Never, rhs: Never) -&gt; Bool {\n    switch (lhs, rhs) {\n    }\n  }\n}\n\nextension Never: Hashable {\n  public func hash(into hasher: inout Hasher) {\n  }\n}\n```</code></pre></div>","timeToRead":2}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/packages/gatsby-remark-codemirror/","id":"f3a10c7f-3995-5616-85d3-052c724f6ce7","layout":"plugins"}}